            {
              "text": "The automotive industry has seen massive gains in productivity thanks to advances in factory automation.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "Implementing factory automation solutions requires careful planning to integrate robotics and software systems.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "Our new assembly line uses state-of-the-art factory automation to ensure consistent quality and speed.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
